<div class='talk-article__body talk-transcript__body'>
<p class='talk-transcript__para'>
<data class='talk-transcript__para__time'>
 0:11
</data>
<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='378' id='t-378'>Hi.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='1645' id='t-1645'>Today I'm going to share
my personal journey</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='4837' id='t-4837'>with female genital mutilation, FGM.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='9838' id='t-9838'>Feel free to cry, laugh, cross your legs,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='13557' id='t-13557'>or do anything your body feels like doing.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='15828' id='t-15828'>I'm not going to name
